    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those seeking a project car or a source for parts. The engine is currently operational but requires major mechanical repairs to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping. The body shows extensive wear, including visible rust, dented panels, and faded paint, while the interior needs a complete overhaul. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources into restoration before this vehicle is fit for daily use.",
